WEBVTT

00:01:29.125 --> 00:01:31.184
Unapenda mikono yangu?

00:01:31.208 --> 00:01:33.518
Inajieleza, ndiyo?

00:01:33.542 --> 00:01:36.018
Sasa tazama mikono yako -- tazama.

00:01:36.042 --> 00:01:38.726
Kuna historia kubwa iliyorekodiwa
kupitia miguso yake.

00:01:38.750 --> 00:01:43.309
na alama za siku za baadaye
kuchorwa katika viganja.

00:01:43.333 --> 00:01:45.143
Kuna wakati mikono hushikilia kwa nguvu,

00:01:45.167 --> 00:01:47.958
wakati mwingine kuachilia.

00:01:49.375 --> 00:01:51.768
Je nikikwambia,

00:01:51.792 --> 00:01:54.292
yote itasambaratika ?

00:01:55.083 --> 00:01:56.476
Mmm

00:01:56.500 --> 00:01:58.226
Mabibi na mabwana

00:01:58.250 --> 00:02:00.768
na wengineo,